📦 Simple E-commerce Product Page
A simple front-end e-commerce interface built using HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, and JavaScript. Users can browse products, view product details in a modal, add items to a cart, and view the cart summary with total pricing.

🖼️ Features
📱 Responsive product cards using Bootstrap grid

🛍️ Add products to cart (JavaScript-based)

🔍 Product detail modal (image, price, rating, description)

🧾 Cart view with item list, quantity, and total price

⚡ Fast, lightweight, and purely frontend (no backend required)

🚀 How to Run
Clone or download the repository.

Open the index.html file in your browser.

Interact with the UI:

Click "Add to Cart" to add items

Click "Cart" in navbar to view cart

Click "View Details" to see more product info

